				choice("Go up the stairs", "Go down the stairs");
				break;
[/code]
[b]Note: If you get a duplicate case error, then change the case id to one that isn't used yet.
But do not forget to change the NpcDialogue = 124 in your StairsHandler to that new Id![/b]



